        <h2 class="title">About Green Haven Project</h2>
        <p class="description">
            The Green Haven Project - Mangrove aims to restore coastal ecosystems and raise awareness
            by planting mangroves and educating participants about the importance of these areas.
            This six-hour event will involve JCI members, local farmers, and students, focusing
            on combating beach erosion and promoting ESG values.
